56:11.818 --> 56:12.819
Wow.

56:12.902 --> 56:13.945
What a... what a clever pun.

56:14.028 --> 56:15.446
That was clever.

56:15.530 --> 56:16.823
I mean, I'm honestly still
kinda pleased with that.

56:16.906 --> 56:18.324
You were poetic.
Yeah, yeah.

56:18.408 --> 56:19.784
"In the sense
