56:32.088 --> 56:33.506
I might've been in
with a chance."

56:33.589 --> 56:34.966
It's all right now.

56:35.049 --> 56:36.342
"Lots of love
and thanks for being cool."

56:36.426 --> 56:37.552
Isn't it nice?

56:37.635 --> 56:39.012
Now, I shall always
treasure that.

56:39.095 --> 56:41.723
- Thank you.
